print("Beloved by", books["Beloved"])
print("Life of Pi by", books["Life of Pi"])
print("The Kite Runner by", books["The Kite Runner"])
print("Never Let Me Go by", books["Never Let Me Go"])

Output:

Books and authors:
The Road by Cormac McCarthy       
Beloved by Toni Morrison
Life of Pi by Yann Martel
The Kite Runner by Khaled Hosseini
